==Description==
The '''Revive''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Revive has a value of 3 [[Diamonds]] {{Diamonds}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Mine Layout==
The Revive appears in the Underground as a 3x3 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:ReviveMine.png|100px]]

==Acquisition==
Revives can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], as [[Rare Hold Items]] from [[File:Zigzagoon.png|30px]] Zigzagoon, and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

